== Events == * {{ill|Yōmyō Tennō|ja|用明天皇}} 元年（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦}} {{ill|585|ja|585}} {{ill|October 3|ja|10月3日}}） – The fourth son of {{ill|Kinmei Tennō|ja|欽明天皇}}, {{ill|Tachibana Toyohihi-no-ōji|ja|橘豊日皇子}}, ascended the throne as the 31st {{ill|Yōmyō Tennō|ja|用明天皇}}. * {{ill|Eikyō|ja|永享}} 元年（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦}} {{ill|1429|ja|1429}} {{ill|October 3|ja|10月3日}}） – To mark the beginning of the reign of {{ill|Go-Kagami Tennō|ja|後花園天皇}}, the era was changed from {{ill|Shōchō|ja|正長}} to {{ill|Eikyō|ja|永享}}. * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政}}5年（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} {{ill|1858|ja|1858}} {{ill|October 11|ja|10月11日}}） – The arrest of members of the {{ill|Sonzōha|ja|尊攘派}} began as part of the {{ill|Ansei no Daigoku|ja|安政の大獄}}. * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治}}4年（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} {{ill|1871|ja|1871}} {{ill|October 18|ja|10月18日}}） – The prefectures of {{ill|Tateno|ja|館県}}, {{ill|Hirosaki|ja|弘前県}}, {{ill|Shichinohe|ja|七戸県}}, {{ill|Hachinohe|ja|八戸県}}, {{ill|Kuroishi|ja|黒石県}}, and {{ill|Tonami|ja|斗南県}} were merged to form {{ill|Hirosaki Prefecture|ja|弘前県}}, thereby defining the modern boundaries of {{ill|Aomori|ja|青森県}}.
== Births == * {{ill|Kōka|ja|弘化}}3年（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} {{ill|1846|ja|1846}} {{ill|October 24|ja|10月24日}}） – {{ill|Amemiya Keijirō|ja|雨宮敬次郎}}, an entrepreneur († {{ill|1911|ja|1911}}).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Genkō|ja|元弘}} 元年/{{ill|Gentoku|ja|元徳}}3年（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦}} {{ill|1331|ja|1331}} {{ill|October 7|ja|10月7日}}） – {{ill|Ashikaga Sadatsuru|ja|足利貞氏}}, a military commander (* {{ill|1273|ja|1273}}). * {{ill|Kōji (Japan)|ja|弘治}}3年（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦}} {{ill|1557|ja|1557}} {{ill|September 27|ja|9月27日}}） – {{ill|Go-Nara Tennō|ja|後奈良天皇}}, the 105th emperor (* {{ill|1496|ja|1496}}). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保}}7年（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} {{ill|1836|ja|1836}} {{ill|October 14|ja|10月14日}}） – {{ill|Saijō Tokunai|ja|最上徳内}}, an explorer of late Edo (* {{ill|1754|ja|1754}}).
