[[Category:Pages to sort]] [[Category:qq]][[de:September 5 (Lunisolar)]][[Category:qq]] [[Category:qq]]{{DEFAULTSORT:September 5 (Lunisolar)}}[[Category:qq]] [[cdo:9 nguŏk 5 hô̤ (nùng-lĭk)]] [[Category:Pages to sort]] [[Category:qq]][[de:September 5 (Lunisolar)]][[Category:qq]] [[Category:qq]]{{DEFAULTSORT:September 5 (Lunisolar)}}[[Category:qq]] [[zh-min-nan:9 goe̍h 5 ji̍t (kū-le̍k)]] [[Category:Pages to sort]] [[Category:qq]][[de:September 5 (Lunisolar)]][[Category:qq]] [[Category:qq]]{{DEFAULTSORT:September 5 (Lunisolar)}}[[Category:qq]] [[zh-yue:九月初五]] {{Lunisolar September}} '''September 5''' is the 5th day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Senshō|ja|先勝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .
== Events == * {{ill|Yōmyō Tennō|ja|Emperor Yōmei|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|585|ja|585|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 3|ja|10月3日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – The fourth son of {{ill|Kinmei Tennō|ja|欽明天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|Tachibana Toyohihi-no-ōji|ja|橘豊日皇子|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , ascended the throne as the 31st {{ill|Yōmyō Tennō|ja|Emperor Yōmei|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . * {{ill|Eikyō|ja|永享|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1429|ja|1429|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 3|ja|10月3日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – To mark the beginning of the reign of {{ill|Go-Kagami Tennō|ja|後花園天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the era was changed from {{ill|Shōchō|ja|正長|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} to {{ill|Eikyō|ja|永享|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 5th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1858|ja|1858|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 11|ja|10月11日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – The arrest of members of the {{ill|Sonzōha|ja|Sonnō jōi faction|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} began as part of the {{ill|Ansei no Daigoku|ja|安政の大獄|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1871|ja|1871|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 18|ja|10月18日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – The prefectures of {{ill|Tateno|ja|館県|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|Hirosaki|ja|弘前県|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|Shichinohe|ja|七戸県|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|Hachinohe|ja|八戸県|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|Kuroishi|ja|黒石県|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , and {{ill|Tonami|ja|斗南県|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} were merged to form {{ill|Hirosaki Prefecture|ja|弘前県|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , thereby defining the modern boundaries of {{ill|Aomori|ja|青森県|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .
== Births == * {{ill|Kōka|ja|弘化|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1846|ja|1846|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 24|ja|10月24日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Amemiya Keijirō|ja|雨宮敬次郎|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , an entrepreneur († {{ill|1911|ja|1911|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Genkō|ja|元弘|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year/{{ill|Gentoku|ja|元徳|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1331|ja|1331|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 7|ja|10月7日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Ashikaga Sadatsuru|ja|足利貞氏|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a military commander (* {{ill|1273|ja|1273|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Kōji (Japan)|ja|Kōji|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1557|ja|1557|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|September 27|ja|9月27日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Go-Nara Tennō|ja|後奈良天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 105th emperor (* {{ill|1496|ja|1496|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 7th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1836|ja|1836|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 14|ja|10月14日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Saijō Tokunai|ja|最上徳内|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , an explorer of late Edo (* {{ill|1754|ja|1754|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
