{{Lunisolar September}} 
'''September 5''' is the 5th day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  day is {{ill|Senshō|ja|先勝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .

== Events ==
* {{ill|Yōmyō Tennō|ja|Emperor Yōmei|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|585|ja|585|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|October 3|ja|10月3日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – The fourth son of {{ill|Kinmei Tennō|ja|欽明天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|Tachibana Toyohihi-no-ōji|ja|橘豊日皇子|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , ascended the throne as the 31st {{ill|Yōmyō Tennō|ja|Emperor Yōmei|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .
* {{ill|Eikyō|ja|永享|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1429|ja|1429|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|October 3|ja|10月3日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – To mark the beginning of the reign of {{ill|Go-Kagami Tennō|ja|後花園天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the era was changed from {{ill|Shōchō|ja|正長|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  to {{ill|Eikyō|ja|永享|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .
* {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 5th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1858|ja|1858|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|October 11|ja|10月11日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – The arrest of members of the {{ill|Sonzōha|ja|Sonnō jōi faction|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  began as part of the {{ill|Ansei no Daigoku|ja|安政の大獄|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .
* {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1871|ja|1871|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|October 18|ja|10月18日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – The prefectures of {{ill|Tateno|ja|館県|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|Hirosaki|ja|弘前県|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|Shichinohe|ja|七戸県|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|Hachinohe|ja|八戸県|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|Kuroishi|ja|黒石県|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , and {{ill|Tonami|ja|斗南県|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  were merged to form {{ill|Hirosaki Prefecture|ja|弘前県|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , thereby defining the modern boundaries of {{ill|Aomori|ja|青森県|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .

== Births ==
* {{ill|Kōka|ja|弘化|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1846|ja|1846|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|October 24|ja|10月24日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Amemiya Keijirō|ja|雨宮敬次郎|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , an entrepreneur († {{ill|1911|ja|1911|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).

== Deaths ==
