* {{ill|Eikyō|ja|永享|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1429|ja|1429|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|October 3|ja|10月3日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – To mark the beginning of the reign of {{ill|Go-Kagami Tennō|ja|後花園天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the era was changed from {{ill|Shōchō|ja|正長|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  to {{ill|Eikyō|ja|永享|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .
