'''September 5''' is the 5th day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September (Nagatsuki)|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  day is {{ill|Senshō|ja|先勝|qq=draft|qq=draft}} .

== Events ==
* {{ill|Yōmyō Tennō|ja|Emperor Yōmei|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|585|ja|585|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|October 3|ja|10月3日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – The fourth son of {{ill|Kinmei Tennō|ja|欽明天皇|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , {{ill|Tachibana Toyohihi-no-ōji|ja|橘豊日皇子|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , ascended the throne as the 31st {{ill|Yōmyō Tennō|ja|Emperor Yōmei|qq=draft|qq=draft}} .
* {{ill|Eikyō|ja|永享|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|1429|ja|1429|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|October 3|ja|10月3日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – To mark the beginning of the reign of {{ill|Go-Kagami Tennō|ja|後花園天皇|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , the era was changed from {{ill|Shōchō|ja|正長|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  to {{ill|Eikyō|ja|永享|qq=draft|qq=draft}} .
* {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 5th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|1858|ja|1858|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|October 11|ja|10月11日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – The arrest of members of the {{ill|Sonzōha|ja|Sonnō jōi faction|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  began as part of the {{ill|Ansei no Daigoku|ja|安政の大獄|qq=draft|qq=draft}} .
* {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 4th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|1871|ja|1871|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|October 18|ja|10月18日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – The prefectures of {{ill|Tateno|ja|館県|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , {{ill|Hirosaki|ja|弘前県|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , {{ill|Shichinohe|ja|七戸県|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , {{ill|Hachinohe|ja|八戸県|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , {{ill|Kuroishi|ja|黒石県|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , and {{ill|Tonami|ja|斗南県|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  were merged to form {{ill|Hirosaki Prefecture|ja|弘前県|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , thereby defining the modern boundaries of {{ill|Aomori|ja|青森県|qq=draft|qq=draft}} .

== Births ==
* {{ill|Kōka|ja|弘化|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 3rd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|1846|ja|1846|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|October 24|ja|10月24日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – {{ill|Amemiya Keijirō|ja|雨宮敬次郎|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , an entrepreneur († {{ill|1911|ja|1911|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ).

== Deaths ==
* {{ill|Genkō|ja|元弘|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  1st year/{{ill|Gentoku|ja|元徳|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 3rd year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|1331|ja|1331|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|October 7|ja|10月7日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – {{ill|Ashikaga Sadatsuru|ja|足利貞氏|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , a military commander (* {{ill|1273|ja|1273|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Kōji (Japan)|ja|Kōji|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 3rd year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|1557|ja|1557|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|September 27|ja|9月27日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – {{ill|Go-Nara Tennō|ja|後奈良天皇|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , the 105th emperor (* {{ill|1496|ja|1496|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 7th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|1836|ja|1836|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|October 14|ja|10月14日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – {{ill|Saijō Tokunai|ja|最上徳内|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , an explorer of late Edo (* {{ill|1754|ja|1754|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ).

