lendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1871|ja|1871|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 18|ja|10月18日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – The prefectures of {{ill|Tateno|ja|館県|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , {{ill|Hirosaki|ja|弘前県|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , {{ill|Shichinohe|ja|七戸県|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , {{ill|Hachinohe|ja|八戸県|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , {{ill|Kuroishi|ja|黒石県|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , and {{ill|Tonami|ja|斗南県|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} were merged to form {{ill|Hirosaki Prefecture|ja|弘前県|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , thereby defining the modern boundaries of {{ill|Aomori|ja|青森県|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} .
== Births == * {{ill|Kōka|ja|弘化|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 3rd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1846|ja|1846|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 24|ja|10月24日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Amemiya Keijirō|ja|雨宮敬次郎|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , an entrepreneur († {{ill|1911|ja|1911|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ).
