* {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ansei|qq=}} 5th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}}  {{ill|1858|ja|1858|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1858|qq=}}  {{ill|October 11|ja|10月11日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 11|qq=}} ） – The arrest of members of the {{ill|Sonzōha|ja|Sonnō jōi faction|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sonzōha|qq=}}  began as part of the {{ill|Ansei no Daigoku|ja|安政の大獄|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ansei no Daigoku|qq=}} .
* {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji era|qq=}} 4th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}}  {{ill|1871|ja|1871|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1871|qq=}}  {{ill|October 18|ja|10月18日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 18|qq=}} ） – The prefectures of {{ill|Tateno|ja|館県|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tateno|qq=}} , {{ill|Hirosaki|ja|弘前県|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hirosaki|qq=}} , {{ill|Shichinohe|ja|七戸県|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shichinohe|qq=}} , {{ill|Hachinohe|ja|八戸県|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hachinohe|qq=}} , {{ill|Kuroishi|ja|黒石県|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kuroishi|qq=}} , and {{ill|Tonami|ja|斗南県|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tonami|qq=}}  were merged to form {{ill|Hirosaki Prefecture|ja|弘前県|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hirosaki Prefecture|qq=}} , thereby defining the modern boundaries of {{ill|Aomori|ja|青森県|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Aomori|qq=}} .

