{{Lunisolar September|qq=}} 
'''September 5''' is the 5th day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September (Nagatsuki)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/September (Lunisolar)|qq=}}  the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}}  day is {{ill|Senshō|ja|先勝|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Senshō|qq=}} .

== Events ==
* {{ill|Yōmyō Tennō|ja|Emperor Yōmei|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yōmyō Tennō|qq=}}  1st year（[[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]]  {{ill|585|ja|585|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/585|qq=}}  [[:en:October 3|October 3]] ） – The fourth son of [[:en:Emperor Kinmei|Kinmei Tennō]] , {{ill|Tachibana Toyohihi-no-ōji|ja|橘豊日皇子|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tachibana Toyohihi-no-ōji|qq=}} , ascended the throne as the 31st {{ill|Yōmyō Tennō|ja|Emperor Yōmei|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yōmyō Tennō|qq=}} .
* [[:en:Eikyō|Eikyō]]  1st year（[[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]]  {{ill|1429|ja|1429|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1429|qq=}}  [[:en:October 3|October 3]] ） – To mark the beginning of the reign of [[:en:Emperor Go-Hanazono|Go-Kagami Tennō]] , the era was changed from [[:en:Shōchō|Shōchō]]  to [[:en:Eikyō|Eikyō]] .
* [[:en:Ansei|Ansei]] 5th year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]]  {{ill|1858|ja|1858|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1858|qq=}}  [[:en:October 11|October 11]] ） – The arrest of members of the {{ill|Sonzōha|ja|Sonnō jōi faction|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sonzōha|qq=}}  began as part of the [[:en:Ansei Purge|Ansei no Daigoku]] .
* [[:en:Meiji era|Meiji era]] 4th year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]]  {{ill|1871|ja|1871|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1871|qq=}}  [[:en:October 18|October 18]] ） – The prefectures of {{ill|Tateno|ja|館県|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tateno|qq=}} , {{ill|Hirosaki|ja|弘前県|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hirosaki|qq=}} , {{ill|Shichinohe|ja|七戸県|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shichinohe|qq=}} , {{ill|Hachinohe|ja|八戸県|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hachinohe|qq=}} , {{ill|Kuroishi|ja|黒石県|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kuroishi|qq=}} , and {{ill|Tonami|ja|斗南県|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tonami|qq=}}  were merged to form {{ill|Hirosaki Prefecture|ja|弘前県|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hirosaki Prefecture|qq=}} , thereby defining the modern boundaries of [[:en:Aomori Prefecture|Aomori]] .

== Births ==
* [[:en:Kōka|Kōka]] 3rd year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]]  {{ill|1846|ja|1846|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1846|qq=}}  [[:en:October 24|October 24]] ） – [[:en:Keijiro Amemiya|Amemiya Keijirō]] , an entrepreneur († {{ill|1911|ja|1911|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1911|qq=}} ).

== Deaths ==
* [[:en:Genkō (1331–1334)|Genkō]]  1st year/[[:en:Gentoku|Gentoku]] 3rd year（[[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]]  {{ill|1331|ja|1331|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1331|qq=}}  [[:en:October 7|October 7]] ） – {{ill|Ashikaga Sadatsuru|ja|足利貞氏|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ashikaga Sadatsuru|qq=}} , a military commander (* {{ill|1273|ja|1273|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1273|qq=}} ).
* {{ill|Kōji (Japan)|1=Kōji (Muromachi period)|2=ja|3=弘治 (日本)|lt=Kōji|4=ru|5=Кодзи (Муромати)|ja|Kōji|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kōji (Japan)|1=Kōji (Muromachi period)|2=ja|3=弘治 (日本)|lt=Kōji|4=ru|5=Кодзи (Муромати)|qq=}} 3rd year（[[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]]  {{ill|1557|ja|1557|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1557|qq=}}  [[:en:September 27|September 27]] ） – [[:en:Emperor Go-Nara|Go-Nara Tennō]] , the 105th emperor (* {{ill|1496|ja|1496|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1496|qq=}} ).
* [[:en:Tenpō|Tenpō]] 7th year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]]  {{ill|1836|ja|1836|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1836|qq=}}  [[:en:October 14|October 14]] ） – [[:en:Mogami Tokunai|Saijō Tokunai]] , an explorer of late Edo (* {{ill|1754|ja|1754|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1754|qq=}} ).

